bash -c '[[ -f "$HOME/.nonshrc" ]] && . "$HOME/.nonshrc"; function prompt { read -rep $'\''\e[35m$\e[0m '\'' input && $input; }; function prompt_msg { [[ $BASH_VERSINFO > 4 ]] || return; gbr=`git branch --show-current 2> /dev/null` && [[ $gbr ]] && gbr=" ($gbr)";echo -e "\e[0;35m`whoami` nonsh \e[0;36m`hostname` `date +%T` \e[0m`pwd`\e[0;35m$gbr" ; }; function nonsh { while true; do prompt_msg; prompt; done } && nonsh'
